        public static AnwInventoryCountingPostDto transform(java.lang.String warehouseCode,
                                    java.util.List<ErpStockDataDto> listOfInventoryCountings)
                                             throws java.lang.Exception
        Method, which will:
        • creates AnwInventoryCountingDto payload from entered warehouse code and list of inventory countings from ERP
        • verifies, whether warehouse and item/SKU exists in SAP Anywhere. If not, they will not be attached to the payload, which will be returned. This provides check against data inconsistencies.
        Parameters:
        warehouseCode - - warehouse code, which exists in SAP Anywhere
        listOfInventoryCountings - - list of inventory counting from ERP
        Returns:
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - - in case when some error
